channel.title: Looking for a website developer!
channel.description:
Hi, Im looking for a website developer for my server. My server is a pi with a lot of updated items such as :nex,tokhaar-kal ect.. If your willing to develope I will give you owner rank in game. Not going to pay any money, because if nobody is willing to do it for owner rank ill just do it myself :D
Reply here if your interested and ill get you some info

item.title: Looking for a website developer!
item.dc:creator: @DaGamerChild DaGamerChild
item.description:
@DaGamerChild wrote:

Time Designing: 1 year
Languages: HTML, Basic PHP, Basic CSS, and RSPS Java ~ I say this because I don’t really know Java, but I can code an RSPS if that makes any sense
Proof of Work: immachrisg is my Skype, if you’re interested I’ll screen share my work.

I’ll only work for you if you can afford to host the server. Otherwise, it’s not really worth my time.
